msgid ""
"ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo "
"dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi "
"jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe "
"anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe:"
msgstr ""
"one, two, three, four, five, ten, twenty, thirty, forty, fifty, a hundred, a "
"thousand, a hundred thousand lives; many eons of the world contracting, many "
"eons of the world evolving, many eons of the world contracting and evolving. "
"They remember: "

msgctxt "dn10:55.7"
msgid ""
"‘amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro "
"evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto."
msgstr ""
"‘There, I was named this, my clan was that, I looked like this, and that was "
"my food. This was how I felt pleasure and pain, and that was how my life "
"ended. When I passed away from that place I was reborn somewhere else. "

msgctxt "dn10:55.8"
msgid "So tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ;"
msgstr "Passing away from there,"

msgctxt "dn10:55.9"
msgid ""
"tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro "
"evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto;"
msgstr ""
"I was reborn elsewhere, and there I had such a name, such a family, such "
"appearance, such food, such experience of happiness and suffering, and such "
"a life-span."

msgctxt "dn10:55.10"
msgid "so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ti."
msgstr "Passing away from there, I was reborn here.’"

msgctxt "dn10:55.11"
msgid "Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati."
msgstr ""
"And so they recollect their many kinds of past lives, with features and "
"details. "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="51"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2.31"></a>
