msgid "Seyyathāpi, māṇava, puriso sakamhā gāmā aññaṃ gāmaṃ gaccheyya;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose a person was to leave their home village and go to another village. "
"From that village they’d go to yet another village. And from that village "
"they’d return to their home village."

#, fuzzy
