msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn10:56.4"
msgid "Tassa evamassa:"
msgstr "They’d think:"

msgctxt "dn10:56.5"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ kho sakamhā gāmā amuṃ gāmaṃ agacchiṃ, tatra evaṃ aṭṭhāsiṃ evaṃ nisīdiṃ "
"evaṃ abhāsiṃ evaṃ tuṇhī ahosiṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘I went from my home village to another village. There I stood like this, "
"sat like that, spoke like this, or kept silent like that. From that village "
"I went to yet another village. There too I stood like this, sat like that, "
"spoke like this, or kept silent like that. And from that village I returned "
"to my home village.’"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn10:56.6"
msgid ""
"So tamhāpi gāmā amuṃ gāmaṃ gacchiṃ, tatrāpi evaṃ aṭṭhāsiṃ evaṃ nisīdiṃ evaṃ "
"abhāsiṃ evaṃ tuṇhī ahosiṃ."
